<plot>A short documentary on hair styles that appeal specifically to women of middle age and the middle class. Elements of sociological inquiry merge with Maddin's customary decayed imagery (obtained naturally by using superannuated home-movie footage) to produce a fascinating and eccentric piece of cinema in the Lumiere Brothers tradition.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?053843</url></doc>
